metadata.name: Treasure hunter no.3
metadata.description:
Welcome to Station 3 ( Valley of Death.)
- This place, it is said that in the center of the valley there are many treasures buried, precious bitcoins and precious stones. But no one who passes by will not survive. Let's help them pass this level. Let's go, treasure hunter.
       Hope you enjoy my imagination and character.
There is also a gift for the winning bidder ❤️❤️
